{
  "info": {
    "name": "FoodFast API Contract Tests",
    "description": "Integration tests for the FoodFast Delivery API.\n\nOrganized by endpoint, with Happy Path and Sad Path subfolders.\nEach test case (TC-xx) may chain multiple requests to tell a complete story.\n\nRun with Collection Runner for end-to-end verification.",
